name: Hyperlapse over LVV
description:
This is my first attempt at this type of shoot. Requires quite a bit of skills and software all new to me. Its not perfect and I have a lot of ideas to improve my next one. This will be a gift to all original collectors of the first 11 pieces. Plus one for myself.

Flying with a DJI Air 2S
Edits done with Luminar 4
Video processing with Wondershare Filmora X
